    "Title": "Red Wind Easy Cargo Recovery",
    "Description": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nOne of our haulers ran into some engine trouble whilst transporting some cargo for us and was forced to abandon their ship. Looking for a contractor who can recover the cargo and complete the delivery. You\u2019ll need to bring your own <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4> to transport the cargo to your ship. Details below.\n\nRECOVERY LOCATION\n     \u00b7 <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>\n\nDROP OFF LOCATION\n     \u00b7 Freight elevator at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>\n\nBe advised, the recovery location hasn\u2019t been verified as safe. You might find an opportunistic outlaw trying to take the cargo for themselves, so be on alert.\n\nTAKE PRIDE IN YOUR WORK \u2013 Even as a contractor you are representing Red Wind Linehaul. Do not intentionally do anything to harm the company\u2019s reputation.",
